data.description:
Welcome to Quotes! Feel free to share any quotes from any author, political figure, fictional character, religious leader, artist, business leader, etc. Quotes can be inspirational, famous, or satirical.

_____


#### Rules

_____

###### POSTS MUST BE QUOTES

Content must either have the title "Quote - Author" (i.e. "My life is my message" - Mahatma Gandhi) or an image with the quote and author. Anything else would be kicked.

_____

###### MARK NSFW FOR QUOTES THAT ARE BASED AROUND

* Antisemitism
* Racism
* Sensitive Political Topics

_____

###### NO HARASSMENT OR THREATS OF VIOLENCE

* Do not harass your fellow users.
* Do not threaten with violence or plan to execute unlawful violent activity and do not encourage others to do so.

_____

###### NO SPAM

_____

###### If you encounter rule-breaking content, report and downvote it.

_____

A member of the non-political guild league: +GuildsOfSubstance

data.description:
Share YouTube channels you enjoy and find recommendations from others.

Please keep posts in this format

[Channel Name] - [Channel Subs] - [Channel Description]

For Example 

Funhaus - 1.67M subs - Comedy gaming channel as well as movie and gaming podcasts.

This will allow me to categorize posts by sub count in the future, so posts not following this naming convention will be kicked to +general and asked to be reposted. 

Feel free to post your own channels but keep it to one post and keep in mind it's in your interest to make the post title easily searchable using keywords etc.

data.description:
Some places on the Internet are stranger than others.  

Post weird things you find while browsing at 2AM. Websites, strange posts, odd YouTube videos, etc.  Dark web addresses are permissible as long as you include a description of the site. 

Know why a certain strange site exists? Even better! Let us know!

Please be safe. Report any unsafe sites! See the pinned post for best practices.

Related Guilds:  
Want something less weird, and more beautiful? +InternetIsBeautiful  
Or are you looking for cooler stuff? +HiddenWebGems  

Rules:  
1- Follow the Ruqqus [Content Policy]([https://ruqqus.com/help/rules). Do not post links to malicious sites.  
2- Posts should be weird and relatively obscure. The less well-known, the better.  
3- Please include warnings in your post title if necessary, e.g. (EPILEPSY WARNING) or (AUDIO WARNING).  
4- Tag any NSFW content as such.  

Rules are subject to change as needed.
